00:57:13.940 --> 00:57:14.940
&gt;&gt; MEIER: Oh, absolutely.

00:57:14.940 --> 00:57:16.890
&gt;&gt; NI-LEWIS: Because it has very nice functionality.

00:57:16.890 --> 00:57:20.760
Kayak, of course is about as consistent as
Hipmunk, well, you know.

00:57:20.760 --> 00:57:22.580
I should've knocked off one more star here.

00:57:22.580 --> 00:57:23.580
&gt;&gt; MEIER: Yeah.

00:57:23.580 --> 00:57:26.600
&gt;&gt; NI-LEWIS: They should've had an action
bar and I really wish they'd get rid of that

00:57:26.600 --> 00:57:30.490
lengthy, lengthy list of all the things that
the app could possibly do.

00:57:30.490 --> 00:57:31.490
&gt;&gt; MEIER: Absolutely.

00:57:31.490 --> 00:57:32.810
