00:57:55.260 --> 00:57:56.260
&gt;&gt; NI-LEWIS: Right.

00:57:56.260 --> 00:57:57.260
&gt;&gt; MEIER: It's probably pretty unlikely.

00:57:57.260 --> 00:57:58.260
&gt;&gt; NI-LEWIS: Exactly.

